Media Query : 
-------------
1. Media query is mainly used to make web page responsive.
2. Here we need to use @media key to define media query.
3. With the help of media query, we can make our web page responsive on various dimensions.
on 360px
on 720px
in between 360px to 540px
in between 720px to 1200px etc
4. Syntax : 
    @media screen | all | print | speech and (max-width:360px)
                                             (min-width:360px) 
                                             (orientation:landscape)
                                             (orientation:portrait)
    {
        ....
    }